Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:46.09,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}察觉时已相依哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:50.06,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}恋情  梦想  鲜花  彩虹  微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:52.62,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}抓紧这一切
